title: Introducing My Senior Project
text: Some of the packages I plan to use: * Forecast: A well known package for forecasting with time series. See: Automatic Time Series Forecasting: The forecast Package for R * Fable: Essentially version three of the Forecast package, but renamed as it now works with tsibbles. See: Fable * FKF: Fast Kalman Filter. See: The Fast Kalman Filter * KFAS: Exponential Family State Space Models in R. * Benchmark: A package for performance comparisons. See: Microbenchmark
